# Functional Requirements

## Lead Management
- Automated lead capture from web forms
- Territory-based lead assignment
- Lead scoring based on budget and timeline
- Email/SMS notifications for new leads

## Property Management
- Centralized property database
- Status tracking (Available/Under Contract/Sold)
- Amenity and feature cataloging
- Image gallery support

## Visit Scheduling
- Calendar integration for agents
- Automated customer confirmations
- Visit feedback collection
- Conflict prevention

## Reporting & Analytics
- Real-time sales dashboards
- Lead conversion funnel
- Agent performance metrics
- Property performance reports